# BDD Spec Framework - Default (Fast Loading)
# Balanced version: Essential features without heavy advanced modules
#
# ✅ Includes: DSL, hooks, matchers, shared examples, let memoization
# ❌ Excludes: Mocking, screenshots, diagrams, gherkin, architecture tests
#
# For advanced features, use: std.spec.adv

